---
import Background from "../components/background/background.astro";
import Globals from "../components/globals/globals.astro";
import SharedStyles from "../components/globals/shared-styles.astro";
import Performance from "../components/globals/performance.astro";
import Navbar from "../components/navbar/navbar.astro";
import SEOHead from "../components/seo/SEOHead.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import bunnysuitImage from "../../public/index/bunnysuit.webp";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <Globals />
    <Performance />
    <SEOHead 
      title="Personal Portfolio"
      description="UCLA Student, Philosophy & Machine Learning Enthusiast. Personal portfolio showcasing research, writing, and projects in AI, philosophy, and mathematics."
      keywords="Leon Lenk, UCLA, machine learning, philosophy, mathematics, research, portfolio, student, AI, artificial intelligence"
    />
    <!-- Performance optimizations -->
    <link rel="preload" href="/fonts/Lora/Lora-VariableFont_wght.ttf" as="font" type="font/ttf" crossorigin>
    <link rel="preload" href="/fonts/Open_Sans/OpenSans-VariableFont_wdth,wght.ttf" as="font" type="font/ttf" crossorigin>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  </head>
  <body>
    <Navbar />
    <Background>
      <Globals />
      <SharedStyles />
      <div class="home-container">
        <div class="hero-section">
          <h1 class="pageName">Welcome</h1>
          <p class="hero-subtitle">Hi, I'm Leon</p>
        </div>

        <div class="main-content">
          <div class="content-grid">
            <div class="image-section">
              <div class="image-card">
                <Image
                  src={bunnysuitImage}
                  alt="My bio pic :)"
                  loading="lazy"
                  quality={85}
                  class="profile-image"
                  decoding="async"
                />
                <div class="image-caption">
                  <svg class="caption-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                    <path d="M12,2A10,10 0 0,0 2,12A10,10 0 0,0 12,22A10,10 0 0,0 22,12A10,10 0 0,0 12,2M12,4A8,8 0 0,1 20,12A8,8 0 0,1 12,20A8,8 0 0,1 4,12A8,8 0 0,1 12,4M12,6A6,6 0 0,0 6,12A6,6 0 0,0 12,18A6,6 0 0,0 18,12A6,6 0 0,0 12,6M12,8A4,4 0 0,1 16,12A4,4 0 0,1 12,16A4,4 0 0,1 8,12A4,4 0 0,1 12,8Z"/>
                  </svg>
                  <span>Me in a bunny suit in a clean room</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="text-section">
              <div class="about-card">
                <div class="card-header">
                  <svg class="header-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                    <path d="M12,4A4,4 0 0,1 16,8A4,4 0 0,1 12,12A4,4 0 0,1 8,8A4,4 0 0,1 12,4M12,14C16.42,14 20,15.79 20,18V20H4V18C4,15.79 7.58,14 12,14Z"/>
                  </svg>
                  <h2 class="card-title">About Me</h2>
                </div>
                
                <div class="about-content">
                  <p class="intro-text">
                    I'm Leon, a student at UCLA. This is my portfolio website. 
                  </p>
                  
                  <div class="interests-section">
                    <h3 class="interests-title">My Favorite Topics</h3>
                    <div class="interests-grid">
                      <div class="interest-item">
                        <span class="interest-number">1</span>
                        <span class="interest-text">Philosophy</span>
                      </div>
                      <div class="interest-item">
                        <span class="interest-number">2</span>
                        <span class="interest-text">Machine Learning</span>
                      </div>
                      <div class="interest-item">
                        <span class="interest-number">3</span>
                        <span class="interest-text">Writing</span>
                      </div>
                      <div class="interest-item">
                        <span class="interest-number">4</span>
                        <span class="interest-text">Math</span>
                      </div>
                      <div class="interest-item">
                        <span class="interest-number">5</span>
                        <span class="interest-text">History</span>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  
                  <p class="content-text">
                    Right now this will mostly serve as a home to all the written content I've produced. At some point
                    I'll also add a section for my projects, for example I have a chess engine that I've been working on for a while.
                    And one day I would also like to add a recipe section as baking has been a passion of mine for a long time.
                    I'm not so good at photography, but I'll try my best to make the recipes look good. 
                  </p>
                  
                  <p class="content-text">
                    At any rate this website is (and probably will forever remain) a work in progress. 
                    I don't expect this site to get much traffic, however if there is something broken please feel free to
                    give me feedback you can email me at <a href="mailto:me@leonlenk.com" class="email-link">me@leonlenk.com</a>.
                  </p>
                  
                  <p class="content-text">
                    Anyway take a look at my pages, I've put a decent amount of effort into this place. 
                    You should also take a look at my friends sites which are linked in the footer. 
                    Have fun and thank you for visiting!
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer-section">
          <a href="https://bulr.boo/" target="_blank" class="neocities-link" data-tooltip="bulr.boo">
            <img alt="Bulr.boo" src="https://bulr.boo/images/badges/bulrboo.png" width="88" height="31" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
          </a>
          <a href="https://peppersalt.neocities.org" target="_blank" class="neocities-link" data-tooltip="peppersalt">
            <img alt="peppersalt" src="https://peppersalt.neocities.org/buttons/PepperSaltedButton.gif" width="88" height="31" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Background>
  </body>
</html>

<style lang="scss">
  .home-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px 60px 20px;
  }

  .hero-section {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
    margin-top: 80px;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin: 0;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .main-content {
    margin-top: 40px;
  }

  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 50px;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .image-section {
    position: sticky;
    top: 100px;
  }

  .image-card {
    background: var(--color-bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-primary);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: 20px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .image-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--gradient-shimmer);
    background-size: 200% 100%;
    animation: shimmer 3s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .profile-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    display: block;
  }

  .image-caption {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 15px;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .caption-icon {
    width: 16px;
    height: 16px;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .about-card {
    background: var(--color-bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-primary);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: 30px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .about-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--gradient-shimmer);
    background-size: 200% 100%;
    animation: shimmer 3s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .card-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 15px;
    margin-bottom: 25px;
    padding-bottom: 15px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-primary);
  }

  .header-icon {
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .card-title {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .about-content {
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .intro-text {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin: 0 0 25px 0;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .interests-section {
    margin: 30px 0;
    padding: 25px;
    background: rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.05);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .interests-title {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin: 0 0 20px 0;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .interests-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .interest-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 15px;
    padding: 10px 15px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    transition: all var(--transition-normal);
  }

  .interest-item:hover {
    background: rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.1);
    transform: translateX(5px);
  }

  .interest-number {
    background: var(--gradient-primary);
    color: white;
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .interest-text {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .content-text {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin: 0 0 20px 0;
  }

  .email-link {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: color var(--transition-normal);
  }

  .email-link:hover {
    color: var(--color-primary-light);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .content-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }

    .image-section {
      position: static;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-section {
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .about-card {
      padding: 25px 20px;
    }

    .card-title {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .intro-text {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .interests-section {
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .interests-title {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    .content-text {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .hero-subtitle {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .about-card {
      padding: 20px 15px;
    }

    .card-title {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
    }

    .interests-section {
      padding: 15px;
    }

    .interest-item {
      padding: 8px 12px;
    }

    .interest-text {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
  }

  .footer-section {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 60px;
    padding-top: 30px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-primary);
  }

  .neocities-link {
    display: inline-block;
    transition: opacity var(--transition-normal);
    margin: 0 10px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .neocities-link:hover {
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .neocities-link img {
    display: block;
  }

  .neocities-link::after {
    content: attr(data-tooltip);
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 100%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
    color: white;
    padding: 5px 10px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    white-space: nowrap;
    opacity: 0;
    visibility: hidden;
    transition: all var(--transition-normal);
    margin-bottom: 5px;
  }

  .neocities-link::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 100%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    border: 5px solid transparent;
    border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
    opacity: 0;
    visibility: hidden;
    transition: all var(--transition-normal);
    margin-bottom: -5px;
  }

  .neocities-link:hover::after,
  .neocities-link:hover::before {
    opacity: 1;
    visibility: visible;
  }
</style>
